snippet.title: Unaligned - Available Now
snippet.description:
Trailer for the videogame Unaligned, developed for the Videogames Creation Master 15th edition from Universitat Pompeu Fabra - Barcelona School of Management.

Download the game at: https://unaligned.gameportfolio.eu/

Artists:
   Jimena Cuenca Bonino
   Nuria Ibañez Miro
   Carlos A. Oporto Jeremías
   Josep Sorribes Ribes

Programmers:
   Juan Pablo Espino Rivero
   Dani Galacho Bermudez
   Cristian Soriano Crespo


Trailer Soundtrack: 
   Fast Motion ( Stephen Daniel Lemaire )
